{"tid":2390621,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"ARK最新個份報告證明左課金GAME將會成為遊戲主流","createTime":"2021-02-01T16:05:06.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-03T08:04:58.000Z","uid":38540,"like":15,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"b4348208b6fac31f88cc7e2f698c4724521addcb","tid":2390621,"uid":38540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T16:05:06.000Z","msg":"可能唔可以再用手機垃圾驚同主機遊戲係兩個市場呢個POINT呃自己<br />\n遊戲課金比例從2010年既20%<br />\n上升到上年2020年佔整體遊戲營收既75%<br />\nARK預計2025年會升到95%既遊戲商營收都係從虛擬商品得來<br />\n呢個係已經變成左不可逆既趨勢<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bcvVLO9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbcvVLO9.png&h=b2fa110f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一次性付費既遊戲產品會買少見少<br />\n好似ONLINE GAME咁逐步變成次文化甚至消失"},{"pid":"7569267bd044601d06e1e1c8ece01a0247adaac7","tid":2390621,"uid":109923,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T16:25:13.000Z","msg":"好多熱門mobile game都係online game<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你係咪想講mmorpg咋？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0acf6f9d8a3c317e958be5ba1a96968ddef8f84","tid":2390621,"uid":14812,"like":5,"dislike":4,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T16:26:24.000Z","msg":"原神<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7329b72292216f363e11f0ae9ea55c70b089f46","tid":2390621,"uid":14812,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T16:29:01.000Z","msg":"在歷經轟動的發行後，聲勢浩大的《原神》在 11 月滑落至營收排名第 3 位，產生約1.43 億美元的營收。而<span class=\"red\">該作品在日本地區的營收最高，以 3,800 萬美元、26.6% 的占比領先中國的 3,630 萬美元（25.4%）</span>。在中國以外的地區，《原神》則以 Google Play 商店為大宗，以 6,500 萬美元（60.7%）居於領先。"},{"pid":"8373d77be9d9adef7d7c455ca946c185da348001","tid":2390621,"uid":109923,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T16:44:25.000Z","msg":"其實全部平台都增長緊<br />\nmobile game只係門檻低，所以draw到更多唔同年齡層嘅玩家<br />\n<br />\n返工長期扮工、長時間通勤、中年人、小朋友呢啲都係mobile game先容易開拓到嘅市場<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0Pejtem.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0Pejtem.png&h=2a4d4ec4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nmmorpg 20年前隨住gaming pc同互聯網普及而崛起<br />\n再加上2010年代後期同質化嚴重，個個都抄wow，冇咗以前百花齊放嘅景象<br />\n之後就俾LOL、食雞等競技game一嘢打沉<br />\n<br />\n不過近年電話效能提升咗好多，開始可以整到複雜啲嘅game<br />\n嚟緊會有越嚟越多mmorpg會跨平台嘅形式重新出現返喺大眾眼前"},{"pid":"fae41625abaf1c010b757413012ccf2ba5acba1b","tid":2390621,"uid":155723,"like":6,"dislike":3,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"a7329b72292216f363e11f0ae9ea55c70b089f46","tid":2390621,"uid":14812,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T16:29:01.000Z","msg":"在歷經轟動的發行後，聲勢浩大的《原神》在 11 月滑落至營收排名第 3 位，產生約1.43 億美元的營收。而<span class=\"red\">該作品在日本地區的營收最高，以 3,800 萬美元、26.6% 的占比領先中國的 3,630 萬美元（25.4%）</span>。在中國以外的地區，《原神》則以 Google Play 商店為大宗，以 6,500 萬美元（60.7%）居於領先。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T19:31:05.000Z","msg":"成個遊戲業比原神搞彎哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d7b9915157169ad332712aa7373ce3055a30ee1","tid":2390621,"uid":114196,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T00:17:51.000Z","msg":"我以為已經係主流<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而家有腦都知整隻課金game仲賺錢<br />\n就算ps4好多單機game都已經有轉蛋/商城系統"},{"pid":"b04f2551b0b3a05eebf0f37d0f63779b26ec2aeb","tid":2390621,"uid":320172,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T00:39:00.000Z","msg":"從來唔玩手機驚，不過得我一個唔玩無用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70b02fc437b64ae90e358ca1eafea436b6d4f020","tid":2390621,"uid":168366,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T00:47:08.000Z","msg":"唔怪得買咁多0700 ADR"},{"pid":"be3268215b297cdc60ced385032887dbf9bb51ac","tid":2390621,"uid":168366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T00:49:09.000Z","msg":"不過Sony一定仲會有3A大作<br />\n啲人係買機去玩隻game<br />\n希望唔會整死小島佢